# Template for a Sinatra Modular Application 
	This repo contains a simple template to write an application using Sinatra. This avoids you to start writting you application from the scrath every time.

## How to use it?
	git clone git@github.com:albertoleal/Sinatra-Template.git
	cd sinatra-template
	rake install_dependencies
	gem install shotgun
	shotgun
	firefox http://localhost:9393/ # This command will a firefox instance and load the page.
